This structure defines the following Slices:

  • The element MedicationKnowledge.code.coding is sliced based on the value of pattern:system
  • The element MedicationKnowledge.doseForm.coding is sliced based on the value of pattern:system

  • The element MedicationKnowledge.intendedRoute is sliced based on the value of pattern:coding.system

  • The element MedicationKnowledge.drugCharacteristic.value[x] is sliced based on the value of type:$this
